V2bg8TrofrBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=f4358bab\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.res.cuhk.edu.hk/zh-tw/applications/current-full-time-undergraduate-students/application-forms/leave-of-absence-suspension-of-studies</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:59:27.000Z","msg":"好～唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望一切順利～"},{"pid":"710ae8f95ead8bf7a4ae563da6e83ce118c27111","tid":1437373,"uid":171530,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"484d93ae9022e8d1f98b3554aa18230bf1021b94","tid":1437373,"uid":62985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"065dd51d4e37d678cadcace9f1a884529839a014","tid":1437373,"uid":171530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cc6a97682df9580c8433b67dfbef324dab0f2c9","tid":1437373,"uid":62985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該唒巴打～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:25:18.000Z","msg":"好難，雖然全家就只有我需要睇psychologist, 但我老母有depression, 老豆脾氣差。屋企拿綜援，一直只能靠政府psychologist同mental dr 跟，自覺根本無用，覺得佢地都係為份糧，無拿個心出黎，講多幾句好似仲覺得我煩。見醫生仲離譜，問我食唔食藥，唔食，一分鐘就叫我出翻去，我有野想講都唔比講.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前升中二，就突然有呢種病，跟住上網搵左個醫生，開d藥都幾好，我可以立即舒緩到，但就有d副作用，後來申請左政府醫生（後生仔，睇落岩岩畢業甘），開左只💊比我，我食左一粒，跟住走左去訓覺，醒左之後，我感覺自己死左甘樣，摸d皮膚好似無感覺，只眼睇野一片黑，跟住嚇到我狂喊，跟住不斷洗面，跟住唔敢睜開眼，直到15分鐘之後無事。<br />\n<br />\n之後我都怕食精神科藥....一直控制住自己情緒，唔敢同人講，真系好痛苦，每日翻學我都比人緊張10倍，但只要無負面思想，我都可以handle到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中學的時候一直低頭唔敢望人，中學d學校老師就覺得我無留心聽書，有d甚至覺得我怪怪地，成個幾鐘，個頭都無向上移過，講真我真系個心跳到想死，想尖叫，個條頸就黎斷，跟住有同學叫我，我仲要扮無事（我成日都怕比人發現）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我因為甘，連早會週會都唔洗去，d同學開始唔中意我，成日問點解你唔洗去，我呃佢地話我腳痛......但明明週會就位坐........我可以點講......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後讀完中學情況好轉左，可能因為知道跟住asso唔洗好似中學甘，但結果又因為asso太chur，而且同左d衰人一組，比人串，有心理陰影.....舊病復發.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97c7e21c74431cda35170b38f60acb5f541754b","tid":1437373,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:31:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"708b6e665a32c505960566fdf2a9b4ec6837e9c4","tid":1437373,"uid":10197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:35:15.000Z","msg":"冇醫生紙都得<br />\n有朋友試過midterm前情緒唔係咁好<br />\n見左prof+OSA 之後交申請表就OK<br />\n可能當年好多人出事所以好易申請<br />\n<br />\n記得交留位費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntake care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b916ec96d45a07683457f413b9296ef6c09d28f","tid":1437373,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},{"pid":"a094359246478b8d42391fe3b2772c1b176e9b71","tid":1437373,"uid":137912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:37:25.000Z","msg":"好似好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d571cf8a88c50d301386108f8e99621855f98e86","tid":1437373,"uid":44277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:40:53.000Z","msg":"建議你留咗位先<br />\n同Department head + student office 講聲<br />\n或者你可以試下話返頭一兩星期睇下點,唔得就休學<br />\n通常到第三星期先真係唔可以停學"},{"pid":"2f17015e4035bf736938dec7cf994626819d7cc0","tid":1437373,"uid":171530,"like":0,"d